Thraxian draconians hail from the village of Thrax in eastern Hyperborea.
While roughly humanoid in shape, they bear a striking similarity to their
dragon cousins, including small, vestigial wings and a fiery breath weapon.
They maintain some of the dragons' raw physical power and intellect as
well. Their alien natures are not well received by other races, and their
clawed hands are not well adapted to using most tools.
